title: The Economist Magazine. 6 - 12 November 2010.
description:
The Economist Magazine. 6 - 12 November 2010.

The Economist is a global weekly magazine written for those 
who share an uncommon interest in being well and broadly 
informed. Each issue explores the close links between domestic
and international issues, business, politics, finance, current 
affairs, science, technology and the arts.
In addition to regular weekly content, Special Reports are 
published approximately 20 times a year, spotlighting a specific 
country, industry, or hot-button topic. The Technology Quarterly, 
published 4 times a year, highlights and analyzes new technologies 
that will change the world we live in. 

Enjoy.
